snippet.title: VGX 2013: Titanfall Ogre Mech
snippet.description:
This is what everyone has been waiting for! Behold the explosive new trailer featuring the Ogre Titan for one of 2014's most anticipated games.

For all the excitement of VGX head over to: http://www.gametrailers.com
